Think of the spiral as being drawn on the usual Cartesian grid with  

 1 at the origin (0,0),  
 2 at (1,0) and afterwards the path going counter-clockwise.
For every lattice point (x , y) put

 k = max{|x| , |y|} (the layer that the point lies on)  
 N(k) = (2k+1)²  (the largest number on that layer, sitting at (k , –k)).

Moving round the square of side 2k in the counter-clockwise direction gives the
number belonging to a point (x , y):

• Bottom edge (y = –k):  n = N(k) – (k – x)  
• Left edge  (x = –k):  n = N(k) – 2k – (y + k)  
• Top edge   (y =  k):  n = N(k) – 4k – (x + k)  
• Right edge  (x =  k):  n = N(k) – 6k – (k – y)

-------------------------------------------------
1.  Position of 2026
-------------------------------------------------
45² = 2025, so 2025 sits at the bottom-right corner of layer k = 22,
i.e. at (22 , –22).  
2026 is the next step to the right, hence at (23 , –22).

-------------------------------------------------
2.  Coordinates of its eight neighbours
-------------------------------------------------
(23,–22) + (dx , dy) with (dx , dy) ∈ {–1,0,1}² \ {(0,0)} gives

(22,–23)  (23,–23)  (24,–23)  
(22,–22)             (24,–22)  
(22,–21)  (23,–21)  (24,–21)

-------------------------------------------------
3.  Value at each of those positions
-------------------------------------------------
Using the formulas above:

(22,–23):  k = 23 (bottom edge) N = 47² = 2209  
 n = 2209 – (23 – 22) = 2208

(23,–23):  k = 23 (bottom-right corner) n = 2209

(24,–23):  k = 24 (right edge) N = 49² = 2401  
 steps = 6·24 + (24 – (–23)) = 191  
 n = 2401 – 191 = 2210

(22,–22):  k = 22 (bottom-right corner) n = 45² = 2025

(24,–22):  k = 24 (right edge)  
 steps = 6·24 + (24 – (–22)) = 190 ⇒ n = 2401 – 190 = 2211

(22,–21):  k = 22 (right edge)  
 steps = 6·22 + (22 – (–21)) = 175 ⇒ n = 2025 – 175 = 1850

(23,–21):  k = 23 (right edge)  
 steps = 6·23 + (23 – (–21)) = 182 ⇒ n = 2209 – 182 = 2027

(24,–21):  k = 24 (right edge)  
 steps = 6·24 + (24 – (–21)) = 189 ⇒ n = 2401 – 189 = 2212

-------------------------------------------------
4.  Sum of the eight neighbours
-------------------------------------------------
2208 + 2209 + 2210 + 2025 + 2211 + 1850 + 2027 + 2212 = 16 952

-------------------------------------------------
Answer
-------------------------------------------------
The sum of all eight neighbours of 2026 is 16 952.
